{
  "scene_id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris",
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_001",
      "speaker": "cordwyn",
      "lines": [
        "They've been mobilizing for weeks. The betrayal\nwasn't a signal — it was a distraction. While we watched Cael\nrun, they marched."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": [
        {
          "line": 0,
          "id": "drums_war"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_002",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "How long do we have?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_003",
      "speaker": "cordwyn",
      "lines": [
        "The Ram hits the eastern wall within the hour.\nWe need everyone on the battlements."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_004",
      "speaker": "caden",
      "lines": [
        "We came. The spirits said to hurry."
      ],
      "condition": "council_result >= 2",
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_005",
      "speaker": "cordwyn",
      "lines": [
        "We hold with what we have."
      ],
      "condition": "council_result == 0",
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": [
        {
          "line": 0,
          "id": "wall_breach"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_006",
      "speaker": "king_aldren",
      "lines": [
        "I was a poor king. I know that. But I will not\nbe a poor man."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_007",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "Your Majesty—"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_008",
      "speaker": "",
      "lines": [
        "(If Edren reaches him first.)"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_009",
      "speaker": "king_aldren",
      "lines": [
        "Edren. The crown... was always too heavy. You\nunderstand that now. Protect... what's left."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_010",
      "speaker": "",
      "lines": [
        "(If Lira reaches him first.)"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_011",
      "speaker": "king_aldren",
      "lines": [
        "The Forgewright... Maren was right. The ley\nlines... should have listened..."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_012",
      "speaker": "",
      "lines": [
        "(If Maren reaches him first.)"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_013",
      "speaker": "king_aldren",
      "lines": [
        "Maren. I should have listened. When you told\nme... about the door..."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_014",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "I know, Your Majesty."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_015",
      "speaker": "king_aldren",
      "lines": [
        "Don't let it... open further..."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_016",
      "speaker": "",
      "lines": [
        "(Default — Edren and party arrive together.)"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_017",
      "speaker": "king_aldren",
      "lines": [
        "Protect... what's left."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_018",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "You are doing wonderfully. Truly. I have not been\nthis entertained in centuries."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_019",
      "speaker": "vaelith",
      "lines": [
        "Rest now. You'll need your strength. The real work\nhasn't started yet."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": [
        {
          "line": 0,
          "id": "pallor_surge"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_19_the_siege_of_valdris_020",
      "speaker": "",
      "lines": [
        "*Everything the party built — every alliance, every trust, every\nplan — burns. The king is dead. The friend is gone. The artifact\nis in the hands of something that wears a familiar face. And the\nPendulum, wherever it is now, is closer to the door than ever.*"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    }
  ]
}
